&lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/sociology/domains/work/texts/formal-structure-of-delegation/>
  rdf:type schema:Article ;
  schema:url &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/sociology/domains/work/texts/formal-structure-of-delegation/> ;
  schema:name "The Formal Structure of Delegation: Presheaves, Heyting Algebras, and Roman Legal Doctrine" ;
  schema:description "A presheaf model of delegation where authority is a sub-Heyting-algebra, accountability non-transfer follows from the directionality of restriction maps, and Roman legal doctrine (nemo dat, delegatus non potest delegare) has precise algebraic content." ;
